{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":false,"flaws":{},"title":"HTMLCanvasElement","mdn_url":"/pl/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement","locale":"pl","native":"Polski","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API\">Canvas API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement\"><code>HTMLCanvasElement</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Własności</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/height\"><code>height</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/mozOpaque\"><code>mozOpaque</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/width\"><code>width</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Metody</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/captureStream\"><code>captureStream()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/getContext\"><code>getContext()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/mozFetchAsStream\"><code>mozFetchAsStream()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/toBlob\"><code>toBlob()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/toDataURL\"><code>toDataURL()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/transferControlToOffscreen\"><code>transferControlToOffscreen()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Events</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/webglcontextlost_event\"><code>webglcontextlost</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Inheritance:</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement\"><code>HTMLElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Element\"><code>Element</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Related pages for Canvas API</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasGradient\"><code>CanvasGradient</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasPattern\"><code>CanvasPattern</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D\"><code>CanvasRenderingContext2D</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ImageBitmap\"><code>ImageBitmap</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ImageBitmapRenderingContext\"><code>ImageBitmapRenderingContext</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ImageData\"><code>ImageData</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/OffscreenCanvas\"><code>OffscreenCanvas</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Path2D\"><code>Path2D</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextMetrics\"><code>TextMetrics</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/createImageBitmap\"><code>createImageBitmap</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\">\n<div id=\"sect2\"></div>\n</div>\n\n<p>Interfejs HTMLCanvasElement zapewnia własności i metody pozwalające na manipulację wygladem i prezentacją elementów canvas. Dodatkowo HTMLCanvasElement dziedziczy własności i metody interfejsu HTMLElement.</p>\n\n<p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"własności","title":"Własności","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>Własności dziedziczone są od rodzica, <a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement\"><code>HTMLElement</code></a>.</em></p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"htmlcanvaselement.height\"><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/height\"><code>HTMLCanvasElement.height</code></a></dt>\n <dd>Wyrażany w dodatniej <code>liczbie całkowitej&nbsp;</code>odpowiada za atrybut <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/canvas\"><code>height</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> elemetu HTML&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/canvas\"><code>&lt;canvas&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> i jest interpretowany&nbsp;w pikselach CSS. Jeśli atrybut nie został określony, lub została przypisana do niego nieprawidłowa wartość, np. negatywna, zostanie użyta domyślna wartość&nbsp;<code>150</code>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"htmlcanvaselement.width\"><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/width\"><code>HTMLCanvasElement.width</code></a></dt>\n <dd>Wyrażany w dodatniej <code>liczbie całkowitej&nbsp;</code>odpowiada za atrybut&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/canvas\"><code>width</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> elemetu HTML&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/canvas\"><code>&lt;canvas&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> i jest interpretowany&nbsp;w pikselach CSS. Jeśli atrybut nie został określony, lub została przypisana do niego nieprawidłowa wartość, np. negatywna, zostanie użyta domyślna wartość&nbsp;<code>300</code>.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"metody","title":"Metody","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>Metody dziedziczone są od rodzica,&nbsp;<em><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement\"><code>HTMLElement</code></a>.</em></em></p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"htmlcanvaselement.capturestream\"><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/captureStream\"><code>HTMLCanvasElement.captureStream()</code></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd>Zwraca&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasCaptureMediaStreamTrack\"><code>CanvasCaptureMediaStream</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, który jest wideo w czasie rzeczywistym z powierzchni elementu&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/canvas\"><code>&lt;canvas&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"htmlcanvaselement.getcontext\"><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/getContext\"><code>HTMLCanvasElement.getContext()</code></a></dt>\n <dd>Zwraca pole robocze elementu <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/canvas\"><code>&lt;canvas&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, lub null jeśli kontekst nie jest wspierany. Pole robocze pozwala na rysowanie na&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/canvas\"><code>&lt;canvas&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>. Wywołanie getContext z atrybutem <code>\"2d\"</code>&nbsp;zwraca obiekt&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D\"><code>CanvasRenderingContext2D</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, natomiast wywołanie z&nbsp;<code>\"webgl\"</code>&nbsp;(lub&nbsp;<code>\"experimental-webgl\"</code>) zwróci obiekt&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebGLRenderingContext\"><code>WebGLRenderingContext</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>. Ten kontekst jest dostepny tylko w przeglądarkach obsługujących WebGL.</dd>\n</dl>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"htmlcanvaselement.todataurl_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/toDataURL\"><code>HTMLCanvasElement.toDataURL()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Zwraca data-URL reprezentujacy obraz w formacie określonym przez parametr&nbsp;<code>type</code>&nbsp;(domyślnie&nbsp;<code>png</code>). Zwracany obraz jest w rozdzielczości 96dpi.</dd>\n <dt id=\"htmlcanvaselement.toblob_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/toBlob\"><code>HTMLCanvasElement.toBlob()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Tworzy obiekt&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Blob\"><code>Blob</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> reprezentujący obraz zawierający się w&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/canvas\"><code>&lt;canvas&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>; ten plik może być buforowany z dysku lub przechowywany w pamięci wedle uznania&nbsp;<code>user agent</code>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"htmlcanvaselement.transfercontroltooffscreen_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/transferControlToOffscreen\"><code>HTMLCanvasElement.transferControlToOffscreen()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd>Przenosi kontrolę do obiektu <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/OffscreenCanvas\"><code>OffscreenCanvas</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, w głównym wątku lub w module roboczym.</dd>\n <dt id=\"htmlcanvaselement.mozgetasfile_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement\"><code>HTMLCanvasElement.mozGetAsFile()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg> <svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n <dd>Zwraca obiekt&nbsp;<a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/File\"><code>File</code></a> reprezentujący obraz zawarty w&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/canvas\"><code>&lt;canvas&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>; plik oparty jest na pamięci, posiada określoną&nbsp;<code>nazwę</code>.&nbsp;Jeśli&nbsp;<code>typ</code>&nbsp;nie został okreslony, domyslnie jest to&nbsp;<code>image/png</code>.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specyfikacja","title":"Specyfikacja","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specyfikacja</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Komentarz</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-fromelement/#html-media-element-media-capture-extensions\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Media Capture from DOM Elements<br><small lang=\"pl\">The definition of 'HTMLCanvasElement' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-wd\">Working Draft</span></td>\n   <td>\n    <p>Dodano metodę&nbsp;<code>captureStream()</code>.</p>\n   </td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/#the-canvas-element\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"pl\">The definition of 'HTMLCanvasElement' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Living Standard</span></td>\n   <td>\n    <p>Metoda&nbsp;<code>getContext()</code>&nbsp;zwraca teraz&nbsp;<a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"The documentation about this has not yet been written; please consider contributing!\"><code>RenderingContext</code></a> zamiast obiektu nieprzeźroczystego</p>\n\n    <p>Dodano metodę&nbsp;<code>transferControlToOffscreen()</code></p>\n   </td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html51/scripting-1.html#the-canvas-element\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML 5.1<br><small lang=\"pl\">The definition of 'HTMLCanvasElement' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recommendation</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html52/scripting-1.html#the-canvas-element\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML5<br><small lang=\"pl\">The definition of 'HTMLCanvasElement' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recommendation</span></td>\n   <td>Definicja początkowa.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Zgodność przegladarek","id":"zgodność_przegladarek","isH3":false,"query":"api.HTMLCanvasElement","dataURL":"/pl/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect3\">\n\n\n<p></p><p></p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"zobacz_też","title":"Zobacz też","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>HTML element implementing this interface: <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/canvas\"><code>&lt;canvas&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>.</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Własności","id":"własności"},{"text":"Metody","id":"metody"},{"text":"Specyfikacja","id":"specyfikacja"},{"text":"Zgodność przegladarek","id":"zgodność_przegladarek"},{"text":"Zobacz też","id":"zobacz_też"}],"summary":"Interfejs HTMLCanvasElement zapewnia własności i metody pozwalające na manipulację wygladem i prezentacją elementów canvas. Dodatkowo HTMLCanvasElement dziedziczy własności i metody interfejsu HTMLElement.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"HTMLCanvasElement","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"HTMLCanvasElement","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"HTMLCanvasElement","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"HTMLCanvasElement","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"HTMLCanvasElement","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"HTMLCanvasElement","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"HTMLCanvasElement","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"HTMLCanvasElement","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"HTMLCanvasElement","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"HTMLCanvasElement","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"pl/web/api/htmlcanvaselement","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pl/web/api/htmlcanvaselement/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web","title":"Technologie Internetowe dla developerów"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/API","title":"Lista Web API"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement","title":"HTMLCanvasElement"}],"pageTitle":"HTMLCanvasElement - Lista Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}